        "desc_en": "Comrade Debobroto Pramanik , was a second year student of Tufanganj , a sub - division in West Bengal . He was SFI sfiwb.org Comrade Debobroto Pramanik , was a second year student of Tufanganj , a sub - division in West Bengal . He was SFI activist and also a member of the Nakkatigach local committee . Criminals of Trinamool Congress attacked and vandalised the local committee office on 11 th of June 2008 as their mode of protest against the Left Front government's developmental policies and industrialisation . Comrade Debobroto was present in the office at that time and tried to restrict these criminals . Unable to digest the fact they were being challenged by a young lad they vented their fury on him and brutally murdered him .",
