        "desc_en": "Comrade Ajay was the son of Sri Syam Prasad and Smt Indira Thankachi of Kollam district Kerala . Com Ajay Comrade Ajay was the son of Sri Syam Prasad and Smt Indira Thankachi of Kollam district Kerala . Com Ajay became a symbol of courage to the young comrades in Karunagapalli . He was the joint secretary of Karunagappalli Area Committee and a delegate in SFI State Conference . He had been in the forefront of the campaign against communal forces and had been instrumental in attracting many students and friends to rally round Left progressive students Union . While working as a Joint secretary of Karunagappalli area committee he had rescued many students from the ABVP /RSS criminals . His activities enraged the RSS goondas . The Fundamentalist and fascist forces found him a threat to their criminal activities and com . Comrade Ajay Prasad was beaten to death on 20 th July, 2007 .",
